dc_title_s: Geologic atlas of Rice County, Minnesota, C-9, Part B, Plate 9, Sensitivity of Ground-Water Systems to Pollution
dc_description_s: Map showing the susceptibility of the ground water system (bedrock and unconsolidated sediments) to contamination,including the age of the water (how long since the water entered the ground), scale 1:100,000, Rice County.
dc_publisher_s: Minnesota Department of Natural Resources, Division of Waters
